ssets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難告到工傷<br />\n一來要醫生紙<br />\n二來就算俾你告得入<br />\n但係要計返你年紀 每個月搵幾多錢<br />\n先計到個賠償金額<br />\n就算計撚埋心靈受創<br />\n賠得幾多俾廢老綜援撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b584a2f8699ffa31a12133397465d9d2f3de99","tid":226271,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"工作壓力使人瘋癲，係咪政府賠先？"},{"pid":"426f12ab4a01c4bcb77d35241e76d8564d2d7ca4","tid":226271,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170502/bkn-20170502190453082-0502_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170502%2Fbkn-20170502190453082-0502_00822_001.html&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KinIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=56e01332\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170502/bkn-20170502190453082-0502_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n他續稱，目前有20多萬領取綜援人士，建議在政府統籌下，「借調」部分齊來參與清潔活動，共同維護公共設施，改善社區環境，倡導香港是我家的概念。他並提及更重要的是，可以協助綜援人士重新走進社區，減低市民之間、甚至與各政府部門之間的隔膜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼有尊嚴過做IT"},{"pid":"c81ae5874e97f3f30f27cbb8cfce64d5b747ee53","tid":226271,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933328431a99df7262c11d4b2b3362f9d1d72ccb","tid":226271,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一向拎綜援都要做一兩日「工作」，去郊野公園掃樹葉，係唔曬嘅樹下每人掃3尺範圍，租旅遊巴車入去，提供午飯，2條以上社工睇住，唔會叫佢哋掃出範圍